item.title: CVE-2023-22022|2024-08-02T09:59:28.789Z -- oracle%20corporation -- life%20sciences%20data%20management%20workbench
item.description: Vulnerability in the Oracle Health Sciences Sciences Data Management Workbench product of Oracle Health Sciences Applications (component: Blinding Functionality). Supported versions that are affected are 3.1.0.2, 3.1.1.3 and 3.2.0.0. Easily exploitable vulnerability allows low privileged attacker with network access via HTTP to compromise Oracle Health Sciences Sciences Data Management Workbench. Successful attacks of this vulnerability can result in unauthorized access to critical data or complete access to all Oracle Health Sciences Sciences Data Management Workbench accessible data. CVSS 3.1 Base Score 6.5 (Confidentiality impacts). CVSS Vector: (CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:L/PR:L/UI:N/S:U/C:H/I:N/A:N).
